---
/**
 * §04 flow — three continuation paths; cold start reloads ledger, not an immortal Invocation.
 */
---

<svg
  class="csr-flow"
  viewBox="0 0 868 268"
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
  role="presentation"
  focusable="false"
>
  <defs>
    <marker
      id="csr-arrow"
      viewBox="0 0 10 10"
      refX="9"
      refY="5"
      markerWidth="6"
      markerHeight="6"
      orient="auto-start-reverse"
    >
      <path d="M 0 1.5 L 9 5 L 0 8.5 Z" fill="var(--accent)"></path>
    </marker>
  </defs>

  <text class="csr-kicker csr-stage csr-stage--0" x="8" y="20" fill="var(--accent)">
    FLOW · THREE CONTINUATIONS · COLD START RELOADS LEDGER
  </text>
  <line
    class="csr-stage csr-stage--0"
    x1="8"
    y1="34"
    x2="860"
    y2="34"
    stroke="var(--hair)"
    stroke-width="1"
  ></line>

  <g class="csr-node csr-stage csr-stage--1" transform="translate(8,52)">
    <rect width="200" height="128" rx="1" fill="var(--bg)" stroke="var(--hair)"></rect>
    <rect width="200" height="2" fill="var(--accent)"></rect>
    <text class="csr-node__idx" x="12" y="26" fill="var(--accent)">01 · AUTONOMOUS</text>
    <text class="csr-node__name" x="12" y="52" fill="var(--ink)">continue / retry</text>
    <text class="csr-node__hint" x="12" y="78" fill="var(--mute)">runTaskOnce again</text>
    <text class="csr-node__hint" x="12" y="98" fill="var(--mute)">project → new Attempt</text>
    <text class="csr-node__hint" x="12" y="118" fill="var(--mute)">optional Runtime replay</text>
  </g>

  <g class="csr-node csr-stage csr-stage--2" transform="translate(228,52)">
    <rect width="200" height="128" rx="1" fill="var(--bg)" stroke="var(--hair)"></rect>
    <rect width="200" height="2" fill="var(--accent)"></rect>
    <text class="csr-node__idx" x="12" y="26" fill="var(--accent)">02 · PARKED</text>
    <text class="csr-node__name" x="12" y="52" fill="var(--ink)">needs_approval</text>
    <text class="csr-node__hint" x="12" y="78" fill="var(--mute)">Inbox · grant facts</text>
    <text class="csr-node__hint" x="12" y="98" fill="var(--mute)">CLI task resume</text>
    <text class="csr-node__hint" x="12" y="118" fill="var(--mute)">then new Attempt</text>
  </g>

  <g class="csr-node csr-stage csr-stage--3" transform="translate(448,52)">
    <rect width="200" height="128" rx="1" fill="var(--soft)" stroke="var(--hair)"></rect>
    <rect width="200" height="2" fill="var(--accent)" opacity="0.7"></rect>
    <text class="csr-node__idx" x="12" y="26" fill="var(--accent)">03 · COLD START</text>
    <text class="csr-node__name" x="12" y="52" fill="var(--ink)">reload TaskEvents</text>
    <text class="csr-node__hint" x="12" y="78" fill="var(--mute)">projectTaskRun()</text>
    <text class="csr-node__hint" x="12" y="98" fill="var(--mute)">budgets stay counted</text>
    <text class="csr-node__hint" x="12" y="118" fill="var(--mute)">≠ revive live handles</text>
  </g>

  <g class="csr-node csr-stage csr-stage--4" transform="translate(668,52)">
    <rect
      width="192"
      height="128"
      rx="1"
      fill="var(--soft)"
      stroke="var(--accent)"
      stroke-dasharray="3.5 2.5"
    ></rect>
    <rect width="192" height="2" fill="var(--accent)" opacity="0.55"></rect>
    <text class="csr-node__idx" x="12" y="26" fill="var(--accent)">TARGET GAP</text>
    <text class="csr-node__name" x="12" y="52" fill="var(--ink)">unified resume</text>
    <text class="csr-node__hint" x="12" y="78" fill="var(--mute)">workspace bytes</text>
    <text class="csr-node__hint" x="12" y="98" fill="var(--mute)">scheduler ownership</text>
    <text class="csr-node__hint" x="12" y="118" fill="var(--mute)">not Current</text>
  </g>

  <g
    class="csr-connectors csr-stage csr-stage--1"
    stroke="var(--accent)"
    stroke-width="1.25"
    fill="none"
  >
    <line x1="208" y1="116" x2="228" y2="116" marker-end="url(#csr-arrow)"></line>
    <line x1="428" y1="116" x2="448" y2="116" marker-end="url(#csr-arrow)"></line>
    <line x1="648" y1="116" x2="668" y2="116" marker-end="url(#csr-arrow)"></line>
  </g>

  <text class="csr-foot csr-stage csr-stage--4" x="8" y="218" fill="var(--mute)">
    Do not collapse the three into one “resume.” Cold start restores control-plane truth from the
    ledger; live world recovery remains Target.
  </text>
  <text class="csr-foot csr-stage csr-stage--4" x="8" y="242" fill="var(--mute)">
    Explicit continuation leaves Task Events — never an in-process implicit loop counter alone.
  </text>
</svg>

<style>
  .csr-flow {
    font-family: var(--sans);
  }
  .csr-kicker {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
  .csr-node__idx {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  .csr-node__name {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 14.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  }
  .csr-node__hint {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
  .csr-foot {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    .csr-stage {
      opacity: 0;
      animation: csr-fade 0.65s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) forwards;
    }
    .csr-stage--0 {
      animation-delay: 0.04s;
    }
    .csr-stage--1 {
      animation-delay: 0.14s;
    }
    .csr-stage--2 {
      animation-delay: 0.28s;
    }
    .csr-stage--3 {
      animation-delay: 0.42s;
    }
    .csr-stage--4 {
      animation-delay: 0.56s;
    }
    @keyframes csr-fade {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .csr-stage {
      opacity: 1;
      animation: none;
    }
  }
</style>
